reviewText:
The Quintet recorded live in 1988 at Heritage USA.  Hi-fi Stereo. Songs included are:

1) I Lean On You, Lord
2) He Is The King
3) Holy Land
4) Let Go And Let God
5) Thanks
6) Holy Highway
7) I'd Do It Over Again
8) When We All Get To Heaven
9) Happy Ending
10) I'll Talk To The Father
11) I've Got A Right

Also includes the award winning concept video:
Famine In Their Land
